He then latches himself onto the roof by grabbing onto the taxi's blue sign and holds on as it continues to make its way across the bridge.

After about 20 seconds, the man climbs down back into the taxi and is commended for his efforts by his friends.

The driver of the taxi is also seen laughing along with the trio as they celebrate the stunt.

But New Zealand police are not amused by the dangerous incident.

